<varlistentry id="options.Bevel">
	<term>Bevel <emphasis remap=´'I'>None|[Left,Top,Right,Bottom,Extra,NoOutline]</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Determines exact size and shape of the 3D bevel drawn around each
        button. This option is somewhat synonymous to NoBorder. If NoBorder is
        encountered after Bevel - then it will override Bevel, otherwise Bevel
        will override NoBorder.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Bevel#synopsis">Bevel flags</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
